<title>Continuous Integration with Jenkins</title>
<section xml:id="page-abstract">
<title>Page Abstract</title>
<para>  Cinder uses a <ulink url="http://jenkins-ci.org">Jenkins</ulink>
  server to automate development tasks. The Jenkins front-end is at
  <ulink url="http://jenkins.openstack.org">http://jenkins.openstack.org</ulink>.
  You must have an account on
  <ulink url="http://launchpad.net">Launchpad</ulink> to be able to
  access the OpenStack Jenkins site.
</para>
<para>
  Jenkins performs tasks such as:
</para>
<variablelist>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <ulink url="https://jenkins.openstack.org/view/Cinder/job/gate-cinder-unittests">gate-cinder-unittests</ulink>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Run unit tests on proposed code changes that have been reviewed.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <ulink url="https://jenkins.openstack.org/view/Cinder/job/gate-cinder-pep8">gate-cinder-pep8</ulink>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Run PEP8 checks on proposed code changes that have been
        reviewed.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <ulink url="https://jenkins.openstack.org/view/Cinder/job/gate-cinder-merge">gate-cinder-merge</ulink>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Merge reviewed code into the git repository.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <ulink url="https://jenkins.openstack.org/view/Cinder/job/cinder-coverage">cinder-coverage</ulink>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Calculate test coverage metrics.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <ulink url="https://jenkins.openstack.org/view/Cinder/job/cinder-docs">cinder-docs</ulink>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Build this documentation and push it to
        <ulink url="http://cinder.openstack.org">http://cinder.openstack.org</ulink>.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
    <term>
      <ulink url="https://jenkins.openstack.org/job/cinder-tarball">cinder-tarball</ulink>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Do <literal>python setup.py sdist</literal> to create a tarball
        of the cinder code and upload it to
        <ulink url="http://cinder.openstack.org/tarballs">http://cinder.openstack.org/tarballs</ulink>
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</article>
</section>
